snippet.textDisplay: Sada Wasda Rawey Saada Sohna Punjab. Opening of this song is with 'Toomba' and I remember when a Faqir used to come to our Pind and would sing a Lullaby to infants while playing this instrument, I was one such kid who got familiar with this sound in my earliest days. My elders migrated from Amritsar, Nangal Saleempur and Nangal Jamalpur. They are also known as 'Nangliye" here in our relatives.
